{
  "logNo": "110165777405",
  "title": "[성장판 확인법/한방성장클리닉/이수성장클리닉] 성장판 닫혀도 키크는 법",
  "addDate": "2013. 4. 8.",
  "categoryNo": "10",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110165777405",
  "html_size": 199150,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110165777405\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110165777405\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_12'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">[성장판 확인법/한방성장클리닉</span><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">]</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">성장판 닫혀도 키크는 법</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">외모를 많이 보는 현대사회에서는 키가 무엇보다도 중요한 요소로 인식되고&nbsp;있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">그래서 오늘은 성장판 확인법에 대해서 준비해 보았습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">보통 키에 대해여 유전적인 요소는 30%이이고 환경적인 것은 70%라고 합니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">즉, 조금만 노력하여 관심을 가진다면 누구나 키가 클 수 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/48a1ab5326f17052.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"504\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 300px; rheight: 504px\" id=\"20130408_248/isuhani_1365389269685gSNB8_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/48a1ab5326f17052.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">하지만 모든 일에는 시기</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">가 있듯이 키크는법에도 시기가 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;키는 성장판이 닫히기 전까지만 크죠 (성장판이 닫힌 후에도 2-3cm 크기도 합니다만.. 일반적인 경우를 말합니다)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">그래서 성장판이 닫히는 시기를 알고 성장판 확인을 하는 것이 중요 한데요</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">오늘은 성장판 확인법 및 성장판이 닫혀도 키크는 법에 대하여 알아보도록 하겠습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b48ec9be6ebd43df.png\" width=\"521\" height=\"487\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 521px; rheight: 487px\" id=\"20130408_42/isuhani_1365389272385WBS8o_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E51.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b48ec9be6ebd43df.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; COLOR: #e97d81; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">성장판 확인법</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">성장판 확인법은 키크는 법을 알고자 하는 사람들이 가장 먼저 확인해봐야 할 부분입니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">특히 성장판이 아직 닫히진 않았지만, 서서히 닫혀가고 있는&nbsp;초등학생 고학년 ~ 중학생이라면 성장판을 확인하는게 더욱 중요하겠죠</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">가장 확실한 성장판 확인법은 X-ray 촬영을 하는 것입니다.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c03a0a2df6142546.png\" width=\"176\" height=\"512\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 176px; rheight: 512px\" id=\"20130408_34/isuhani_1365389274864HoDKv_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E53.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c03a0a2df6142546.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">성장판은 자가진단을&nbsp;통해 지금의 상태를 알 수 없습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">아래의 성장장애 자가진단 기준을 확인해서 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;내용 중 4개 이상 포함된다면 성장장애를 의심하고, X-ray 검사를 통해 성장판의 상태를 확인해야합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">예를 들어 아이의 나이가 10살인데, 뼈나이는 12살, 13살로 확인될 수 있습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">이처럼 자기 나이보다&nbsp;성장판이 일찍 닫히는 경우에는 최종키가 작을 수 있답니다.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f5941731e23c9748.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"522\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 264px; rheight: 522px\" id=\"20130408_77/isuhani_1365389277177DXk22_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E54.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f5941731e23c9748.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; COLOR: #e97d81; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;성장장애&nbsp; 자가진단</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 아토피성 피부염이나 알레르기 비염이 있다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 자녀의 키가 자녀보다 두살 어린 아이보다 작다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 평소에 음식을 잘 ㅗ먹지 않는다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 뛰어 노는 것에 흥미가 없고 마른체형이다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 수면이 부족하고하고 깊은 잠을 취하지 못한다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 일년에 키가 4cm이상 자라지 않는다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 인스턴트 음식을 자주 섭취하고 편식하는 편이다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 출생 시 미숙아 또는 조기 출산을 했다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 작년에 입었던 옷이 지금입어도 작아지</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">지 않는다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 유아표준신장과 비교했 때 평균키보다 10cm이상 작다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 자주 불안하고 스트레스를 많이 받는 편이다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 자주 배가 아프고 설사나 변비가 있다</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7c1df855b82cf007.png\" width=\"238\" height=\"494\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 238px; rheight: 494px\" id=\"20130408_278/isuhani_1365389279645PYnTA_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E55.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7c1df855b82cf007.png\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; COLOR: #e97d81; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">성장판이 닫혀도 키크는법</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">이왕이면 성장판이 닫히기 전에 키가 클 수 있도록 환경을 조성해주는 것이 좋습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">하지만 위에 잠깐 언급했듯이&nbsp;성장판이 닫혀도 키크는 경우가 있으니 완전히 포기할 단계는 아닙니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">요즘에는 의학의 힘을 빌려서 성장판이 닫혀도 키크는 법이 있기도 합니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">한방성장클리닉 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">에서는 척추를 바르게 교정하는 추나요법을 통해 숨어있는 2cm 를 찾아 줍니다. </span><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/57eb6070997a302a.png\" width=\"364\" height=\"517\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 364px; rheight: 517px\" id=\"20130408_168/isuhani_1365389284966IjqkH_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E57.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/57eb6070997a302a.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">성장판이&nbsp;완전히 닫히기 전에&nbsp;키가 클려면 우리가 섭취하는 음식이나 운동에 대하여 신경을 많이 써야합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">기본적으인 방법으로는 성장에 방해되는 밀가루,인스턴트,튀김등을 줄이고 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;영양소를&nbsp;골고루&nbsp;섭취 해야하는데요</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">야채,단백질이 풍부한 고기,생선이나 두부 등을 우선으로&nbsp;섭취&nbsp;합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">성장판이 완전히&nbsp;닫힌 후에도 역시나 음식을 신경써서 섭취를 해야 하고, </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">그 뿐 아니라 바른자세를&nbsp;위한 노력해도 필요합니다.&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">구부정한 자세를 반듯하게 펴준다면 키가 조금 더 클 수 있기 때문입니다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3ab2c0eaf4c28ec5.png\" width=\"396\" height=\"526\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 396px; rheight: 526px\" id=\"20130408_47/isuhani_1365389287913DYCN0_PNG/%C5%B0%BC%BA%C0%E58.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3ab2c0eaf4c28ec5.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><u>한방성장클리닉 이수한의원에서는</u></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">&nbsp; 척추와 골반을 바르게 교정하고 아이들 개개인에&nbsp;맞는 맞춤처방을 합니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\">또한 성장상담을 통해 식이요법과</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"> 운동요법에 대해 알아 볼 수 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><div>\n<iframe src=\"https://mashup.map.naver.com/view.nhn?mid=bl013116867%40s13104608&type=total\" width=\"402\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" onerror=\"return true;\" onabort=\"return true;\" style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:8px;background-color:white;\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 지도\"></iframe>\n</div></div>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #00b0a2\">이수한의원 진료시간 안내</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b26b65168c0499d6.png\" width=\"547\" height=\"172\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 547px; rheight: 172px\" id=\"20130408_74/isuhani_1365391067926Ki0dQ_PNG/%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3%C7%A52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b26b65168c0499d6.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #00b0a2\">이수한의원 </span><span style=\"COLOR: #00b0a2\">상담전화 02)584 -1075</span><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></strong><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/11b9c4d6a52cce98.png\" width=\"266\" height=\"66\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 266px; rheight: 66px\" id=\"20130408_191/isuhani_1365391070350525or_PNG/2013-03-18_14%3B49%3B33.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6645BFD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/11b9c4d6a52cce98.png\"></p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
